name: Antonio Lorenzo
description: I am real easy person to talk to and a good listener. I love working, playing golf, reading news papers swimming like going to the beach, walking, watching football and athletics go to gym. I’m very friendly, open minded and straight forward in life, loving and caring person who knows how to take very good care of a woman especially giving her sense of belonging in everything I do in life. I am very quiet at first but I warm up quickly, communication is very important to me I love animals a lots especially dogs and cats.
